ðŸ’¥ LDR Sensor Module Interface With Arduino
(LED Light & Traffic Light Arduino Script Code)

ðŸŒ· Device Needs : 
1) Arduino Board
2) LDR Sensor Module
3) Jumper Wires

ðŸŒ· Connection Ports :
Aurdino(analog & power)Port <-> LDR Sensor Port
gnd - gnd
5v - vcc
A1 - A1

ðŸŒ· Arduino Code : 
__________

int ldr;  //Set A0(Analog Input) for LDR.
//int value=0;
void setup()
pinMode(13,OUTPUT);
Serial.begin(9600);
//pinMode(3,OUTPUT);
void loop()
{
ldr = analogRead(A0);  //Reads the Value-of LDR(light).
if(ldr<50)
{
   digitalWrite(13, HIGH);
}
else
{
   digitalwrite(13, LOW);
}
Serial.println(ldr);  //prints the value of LDR to Serial Monitor.
delay(100);
}
//Serial.println(value);

